metadata.name: Brilliance
metadata.description:
I created this work to express a "beautiful and shining woman.

Beauty is not just about appearance.
I believe that beauty is not only about appearance, but also about the strength and kindness that overflows from within, and the radiance that comes from accumulated effort and experience.

I chose rubies for her accessories.
It is said that its fiery red color has the power to bring out the inner charm of a woman.
